# Copy to .env.local to enable real AI problem generation + free-form grading.
# Pick ONE provider. Without either, Proofer runs in "demo mode".

# --- Free option (recommended): Google Gemini ---------------------------------
# Get a free key (no credit card) at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# If this is set, Proofer uses Gemini and ignores the Anthropic key below.
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model (default gemini-2.0-flash, which is on the free tier)
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash

# --- Paid option: Anthropic Claude (best grading quality) ---------------------
# Needs a FUNDED account at console.anthropic.com → Plans & Billing.
# A Claude Pro/Max subscription does NOT fund this — it's separate, pay-as-you-go.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
